cold eyes ( hangul : 감시자들 ; rr : gamsijadeul ; lit . " stakeout " or " surveillance " ) is a 2013 south korean film starring sol kyung-gu , jung woo-sung , han hyo-joo , jin kyung and lee junho . a remake of 2007 hong kong film eye in the sky , the film is about detectives from the surveillance team of a special crime unit who work together to take down a bank robbing organization . it made its north american premiere at the 2013 toronto international film festival , and also screened at the 2013 busan international film festival in the open cinema section .